<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <style>
        body {
            color: #000;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 640px;
            margin: auto;
        }
        .card {
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            /* width: 640px; */
            height: 80%;
            /* margin: auto; */
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
        }        .image {
            padding-top: 50px;
            display: block;
        }
        .text-center {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .wrapper {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            color: #000;
        }
        .decoration {
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .magic-link {
            color: white;
            background-color: blue;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 10px;
            display: inline-block;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 300px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .magic-link {
            width: auto;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }
        .color-black {
            color: #000;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body style="background-color: #ddd; width: 100%">
    <div class="container">
        <%- include('./header.ejs') %>
            <hr style="margin:0" />
            <div class="card">
                <h4 class="color-black"><b>Greetings from Scaffold</b></h4>
                <h4 class="color-black">Dear <%= firstName %> <%= lastName %>,</h4>
                <p class="color-black">We are writing to confirm that your password for our website has been changed successfully. If you did not request this change, please <a href="#" target="_blank">contact us </a>immediately.</p>
                <div class="wrapper">
                    <p class="color-black">We take the security of your account very seriously, and we encourage you to choose a strong, unique password that is not easily guessed or shared with others.</p>
                        
                    </p>
                    <p class="color-black">If you experience any issues accessing your account or have any other concerns, please do not hesitate to <a href="#" target="_blank">contact us </a> We appreciate your prompt attention to this matter.</p>
          
                    <p class="color-black">Best Regards,</p>
                    <p class="color-black"><b>Scaffold Team</b></p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <hr style="margin:0" />
            <%- include('./footer.ejs') %>
    </div>
</body>

</html>